{
  "id": "nn_moir8bas_fykahdm5s",
  "title": "ENGLISH UNIT 4",
  "content": "\n\n<h1 data-end=\"189\" data-start=\"146\" data-section-id=\"x56nfk\">📘 PART 1: Referencing and Writing Skills</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"214\" data-start=\"191\" data-section-id=\"aaokas\">What is Referencing?</h2>\n<p data-end=\"318\" data-start=\"216\">Referencing means giving credit to the books, websites, journals, or reports you used in your writing.</p>\n<p data-end=\"332\" data-start=\"320\">👉 It shows:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"417\" data-start=\"333\">\n<li data-end=\"361\" data-start=\"333\" data-section-id=\"11bbqlx\">\nYour information is real\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"382\" data-start=\"362\" data-section-id=\"10j5l17\">\nYou did research\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"417\" data-start=\"383\" data-section-id=\"1wtn48r\">\nYou are not copying (plagiarism)\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-end=\"431\" data-start=\"419\" data-section-id=\"1wxcevo\">Example:</h3>\n<p data-end=\"464\" data-start=\"432\">If you use a book by John Smith:</p>\n<p data-end=\"494\" data-start=\"466\"><strong data-end=\"478\" data-start=\"466\">In text:</strong><br data-end=\"481\" data-start=\"478\">\n(Smith, 2023)</p>\n<p data-end=\"586\" data-start=\"496\"><strong data-end=\"525\" data-start=\"496\">At end in reference list:</strong><br data-end=\"528\" data-start=\"525\">\nSmith, J. (2023). <em data-end=\"571\" data-start=\"546\">Learning Writing Skills</em>. Oxford Press.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"591\" data-start=\"588\">\n<h1 data-end=\"633\" data-start=\"593\" data-section-id=\"1nnpkt0\">📘 PART 2: Types of Referencing Styles</h1>\n<p data-end=\"675\" data-start=\"635\">Different colleges use different styles.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"696\" data-start=\"677\" data-section-id=\"orrss7\">1. Harvard Style</h2>\n<p data-end=\"719\" data-start=\"697\">Uses <strong data-end=\"719\" data-start=\"702\">Author + Year</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"745\" data-start=\"721\">Example:<br data-end=\"732\" data-start=\"729\">\n(Smith, 2023)</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"762\" data-start=\"747\" data-section-id=\"evj91a\">2. APA Style</h2>\n<p data-end=\"821\" data-start=\"763\">Same as Harvard, mostly used in psychology/social science.</p>\n<p data-end=\"853\" data-start=\"823\">Example:<br data-end=\"834\" data-start=\"831\">\n(Smith, 2023, p.15)</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"870\" data-start=\"855\" data-section-id=\"1p061fz\">3. MLA Style</h2>\n<p data-end=\"900\" data-start=\"871\">Uses <strong data-end=\"900\" data-start=\"876\">Author + Page Number</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"923\" data-start=\"902\">Example:<br data-end=\"913\" data-start=\"910\">\n(Smith 15)</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"944\" data-start=\"925\" data-section-id=\"115y4m8\">4. Chicago Style</h2>\n<p data-end=\"978\" data-start=\"945\">Uses footnotes at bottom of page.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1023\" data-start=\"980\">Example:<br data-end=\"991\" data-start=\"988\">\n¹ John Smith, <em data-end=\"1016\" data-start=\"1005\">Book Name</em> (2023)</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"1046\" data-start=\"1025\" data-section-id=\"14edh54\">5. Vancouver Style</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1060\" data-start=\"1047\">Uses numbers.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1076\" data-start=\"1062\">Example:<br data-end=\"1073\" data-start=\"1070\">\n(1)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1081\" data-start=\"1078\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1110\" data-start=\"1083\" data-section-id=\"62j3of\">📘 PART 3: Book Reference</h1>\n<p data-end=\"1132\" data-start=\"1112\">If source is a book:</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"1153\" data-start=\"1134\" data-section-id=\"1ewf7n1\">Harvard Example:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1218\" data-start=\"1155\">Smith, J. (2023). <em data-end=\"1202\" data-start=\"1173\">The Psychology of Happiness</em>. London: Wiley.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"1235\" data-start=\"1220\" data-section-id=\"1dq7xxj\">APA Example:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1292\" data-start=\"1237\">Smith, J. (2023). <em data-end=\"1284\" data-start=\"1255\">The Psychology of Happiness</em>. Wiley.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1297\" data-start=\"1294\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1329\" data-start=\"1299\" data-section-id=\"1h22emo\">📘 PART 4: Journal Reference</h1>\n<p data-end=\"1357\" data-start=\"1331\">Journal = research article</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"1370\" data-start=\"1359\" data-section-id=\"q0rqlz\">Example:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1462\" data-start=\"1372\">Smith, J. (2023). Impact of technology on education. <em data-end=\"1447\" data-start=\"1425\">Journal of Education</em>, 12(2), 10-25.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1467\" data-start=\"1464\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1499\" data-start=\"1469\" data-section-id=\"146uz8r\">📘 PART 5: Website Reference</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"1520\" data-start=\"1501\" data-section-id=\"1ppa0od\">Example Harvard:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1611\" data-start=\"1522\">Smith, J. (2023). Benefits of Exercise. Available at: <a target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-end=\"1587\" data-start=\"1576\">www.xyz.com<svg data-rtl-flip=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"></svg></a> (Accessed 4 April 2025)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1616\" data-start=\"1613\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1647\" data-start=\"1618\" data-section-id=\"9b51fh\">📘 PART 6: Report Reference</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"1660\" data-start=\"1649\" data-section-id=\"q0rqlz\">Example:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1749\" data-start=\"1662\">Bedford, D. (2017). <em data-end=\"1719\" data-start=\"1682\">Enterprise Information Architecture</em>. Washington State Department.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1754\" data-start=\"1751\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1795\" data-start=\"1756\" data-section-id=\"eqn61s\">📘 PART 7: Explanation vs Elucidation</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"1826\" data-start=\"1797\" data-section-id=\"9lyrk2\">Explanation = Easy Meaning</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1858\" data-start=\"1828\">Used to make something simple.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1918\" data-start=\"1860\">Example:<br data-end=\"1871\" data-start=\"1868\">\nCloud computing means storing data on internet.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"1949\" data-start=\"1920\" data-section-id=\"1botpxg\">Elucidation = Deep Meaning</h2>\n<p data-end=\"1977\" data-start=\"1951\">Used to explain in detail.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2083\" data-start=\"1979\">Example:<br data-end=\"1990\" data-start=\"1987\">\nCloud computing gives online storage, servers, apps. It saves money and helps companies grow.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2100\" data-start=\"2085\">👉 Short trick:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2156\" data-start=\"2102\">\n<li data-end=\"2127\" data-start=\"2102\" data-section-id=\"56xm2k\">\n<strong data-end=\"2127\" data-start=\"2104\">Explanation = Basic</strong>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2156\" data-start=\"2128\" data-section-id=\"sih562\">\n<strong data-end=\"2156\" data-start=\"2130\">Elucidation = Detailed</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2161\" data-start=\"2158\">\n<h1 data-end=\"2193\" data-start=\"2163\" data-section-id=\"ix9fc3\">📘 PART 8: Effective Writing</h1>\n<p data-end=\"2241\" data-start=\"2195\">Good writing means reader understands quickly.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"2256\" data-start=\"2243\" data-section-id=\"1u8g7xw\">Qualities:</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2258\" data-section-id=\"1xelt9g\">1. Accuracy</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2292\" data-start=\"2274\">Use correct facts.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2337\" data-start=\"2294\">❌ Machine gets hot<br data-end=\"2315\" data-start=\"2312\">\n✅ Machine reaches 75°C</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"2353\" data-start=\"2339\" data-section-id=\"pjm5k2\">2. Clarity</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2371\" data-start=\"2354\">Use simple words.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2413\" data-start=\"2373\">❌ It kind of works<br data-end=\"2394\" data-start=\"2391\">\n✅ It works properly</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"2435\" data-start=\"2415\" data-section-id=\"7665va\">3. Logical Order</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2452\" data-start=\"2437\">Write in order:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2492\" data-start=\"2454\">\n<li data-end=\"2470\" data-start=\"2454\" data-section-id=\"19ezcso\">\nIntroduction\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2479\" data-start=\"2471\" data-section-id=\"1vh0fko\">\nBody\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2492\" data-start=\"2480\" data-section-id=\"k9f963\">\nConclusion\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-end=\"2512\" data-start=\"2494\" data-section-id=\"1l6m28i\">4. Objectivity</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2538\" data-start=\"2514\">Use facts, not emotions.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2597\" data-start=\"2540\">❌ I think this is best<br data-end=\"2565\" data-start=\"2562\">\n✅ Test results show this is best</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2602\" data-start=\"2599\">\n<h1 data-end=\"2639\" data-start=\"2604\" data-section-id=\"1usuod1\">📘 PART 9: Vocabulary Improvement</h1>\n<p data-end=\"2687\" data-start=\"2641\">Use better words instead of simple weak words.</p>\n<div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><table data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2689\"><thead data-end=\"2716\" data-start=\"2689\"><tr data-end=\"2716\" data-start=\"2689\"><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2701\" data-start=\"2689\">Weak Word</th><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2716\" data-start=\"2701\">Better Word</th></tr></thead><tbody data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2742\"><tr data-end=\"2762\" data-start=\"2742\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2749\" data-start=\"2742\">Good</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2762\" data-start=\"2749\">Efficient</td></tr><tr data-end=\"2779\" data-start=\"2763\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2769\" data-start=\"2763\">Bad</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2779\" data-start=\"2769\">Faulty</td></tr><tr data-end=\"2798\" data-start=\"2780\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2788\" data-start=\"2780\">Thing</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2798\" data-start=\"2788\">Device</td></tr><tr data-end=\"2817\" data-start=\"2799\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2806\" data-start=\"2799\">Make</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2817\" data-start=\"2806\">Develop</td></tr><tr data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2818\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2823\" data-start=\"2818\">Do</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2823\">Perform</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<p data-end=\"2844\" data-start=\"2836\">Example:</p>\n<p data-end=\"2908\" data-start=\"2846\">❌ Software is good<br data-end=\"2867\" data-start=\"2864\">\n✅ Software is efficient and user-friendly</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2913\" data-start=\"2910\">\n<h1 data-end=\"2947\" data-start=\"2915\" data-section-id=\"1dx1e0r\">📘 PART 10: Sentence Structure</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"2970\" data-start=\"2949\" data-section-id=\"arhtit\">Types of Sentences</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2983\" data-start=\"2972\" data-section-id=\"1eird1u\">Simple:</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3008\" data-start=\"2984\">The software works fast.</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"3023\" data-start=\"3010\" data-section-id=\"16n56jh\">Compound:</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3070\" data-start=\"3024\">The software works fast, but uses more memory.</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"3084\" data-start=\"3072\" data-section-id=\"1amx18\">Complex:</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3130\" data-start=\"3085\">Because it uses more memory, it is expensive.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3135\" data-start=\"3132\">\n<h1 data-end=\"3170\" data-start=\"3137\" data-section-id=\"17eqye2\">📘 PART 11: Brevity and Clarity</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"3202\" data-start=\"3172\" data-section-id=\"1on0noi\">Brevity = Use fewer words</h2>\n<h2 data-end=\"3234\" data-start=\"3203\" data-section-id=\"jo60sx\">Clarity = Easy to understand</h2>\n<p data-end=\"3306\" data-start=\"3236\">❌ Due to the fact that machine failed...<br data-end=\"3279\" data-start=\"3276\">\n✅ Because machine failed...</p>\n<p data-end=\"3366\" data-start=\"3308\">❌ In order to improve efficiency<br data-end=\"3343\" data-start=\"3340\">\n✅ To improve efficiency</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3371\" data-start=\"3368\">\n<h1 data-end=\"3409\" data-start=\"3373\" data-section-id=\"8dd0qq\">📘 PART 12: Cohesion and Coherence</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"3451\" data-start=\"3411\" data-section-id=\"1m7zku1\">Cohesion = Sentences connect smoothly</h2>\n<p data-end=\"3471\" data-start=\"3453\">Use linking words:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"3521\" data-start=\"3473\">\n<li data-end=\"3486\" data-start=\"3473\" data-section-id=\"37pv3s\">\nTherefore\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3498\" data-start=\"3487\" data-section-id=\"1mpvkf0\">\nHowever\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3507\" data-start=\"3499\" data-section-id=\"1w85dg9\">\nAlso\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3521\" data-start=\"3508\" data-section-id=\"rkiydu\">\nAs a result\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"3531\" data-start=\"3523\">Example:</p>\n<p data-end=\"3594\" data-start=\"3533\">Automation saves time. <strong data-end=\"3571\" data-start=\"3556\">As a result</strong>, production increases.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3599\" data-start=\"3596\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3636\" data-start=\"3601\" data-section-id=\"yoor9x\">Coherence = Ideas in right order</h2>\n<p data-end=\"3642\" data-start=\"3638\">Bad:</p>\n<p data-end=\"3694\" data-start=\"3644\">Cloud is popular. Cars are fast. Security matters.</p>\n<p data-end=\"3701\" data-start=\"3696\">Good:</p>\n<p data-end=\"3752\" data-start=\"3703\">Cloud is popular. However, security is important.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3757\" data-start=\"3754\">\n<h1 data-end=\"3792\" data-start=\"3759\" data-section-id=\"1ymrdl7\">📘 PART 13: Emphasis in Writing</h1>\n<p data-end=\"3842\" data-start=\"3794\">Emphasis means making important point stand out.</p>\n<p data-end=\"3852\" data-start=\"3844\">Example:</p>\n<p data-end=\"3945\" data-start=\"3854\">❌ Efficiency increased.<br data-end=\"3880\" data-start=\"3877\">\n✅ The most important result was a <strong data-end=\"3944\" data-start=\"3914\">45% increase in efficiency</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"3951\" data-start=\"3947\">Use:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"3997\" data-start=\"3952\">\n<li data-end=\"3958\" data-start=\"3952\" data-section-id=\"1j41ux9\">\nBold\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3982\" data-start=\"3959\" data-section-id=\"rpf62x\">\nImportant words first\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3997\" data-start=\"3983\" data-section-id=\"1f524vm\">\nActive voice\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"4002\" data-start=\"3999\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4035\" data-start=\"4004\" data-section-id=\"1n4cozh\">📘 PART 14: Paragraph Writing</h1>\n<p data-end=\"4082\" data-start=\"4037\">A paragraph = group of sentences on one idea.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4097\" data-start=\"4084\" data-section-id=\"1k0g8ay\">Structure:</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"4120\" data-start=\"4099\" data-section-id=\"lwwo1l\">1. Topic Sentence</h3>\n<p data-end=\"4137\" data-start=\"4121\">Tells main idea.</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"4166\" data-start=\"4139\" data-section-id=\"15wiaqv\">2. Supporting Sentences</h3>\n<p data-end=\"4189\" data-start=\"4167\">Give details/examples.</p>\n<h3 data-end=\"4217\" data-start=\"4191\" data-section-id=\"m31pcp\">3. Conclusion Sentence</h3>\n<p data-end=\"4233\" data-start=\"4218\">Ends paragraph.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4246\" data-start=\"4235\" data-section-id=\"q0rqlz\">Example:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4354\" data-start=\"4248\">Online learning is useful. It saves travel time and gives flexibility. Therefore, many students prefer it.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"4359\" data-start=\"4356\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4386\" data-start=\"4361\" data-section-id=\"sn77ze\">📘 Easy Revision Tricks</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"4403\" data-start=\"4388\" data-section-id=\"yp7nbl\">Referencing:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4428\" data-start=\"4404\">Giving credit to source.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4445\" data-start=\"4430\" data-section-id=\"sosf9o\">Explanation:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4461\" data-start=\"4446\">Simple meaning.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4478\" data-start=\"4463\" data-section-id=\"k3xbn4\">Elucidation:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4496\" data-start=\"4479\">Detailed meaning.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4519\" data-start=\"4498\" data-section-id=\"1lghu0a\">Effective Writing:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4548\" data-start=\"4520\">Clear + Correct + Organized.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4561\" data-start=\"4550\" data-section-id=\"coxhbs\">Brevity:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4576\" data-start=\"4562\">Short writing.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4591\" data-start=\"4578\" data-section-id=\"4tdw75\">Coherence:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4618\" data-start=\"4592\">Ideas connected logically.</p>\n<h2 data-end=\"4633\" data-start=\"4620\" data-section-id=\"1nbjqmp\">Paragraph:</h2>\n<p data-end=\"4661\" data-start=\"4634\">One main idea in one block.</p>\n\n\n",
